      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The city council has approved\nasphalt paving for the big Brownies\naddition job, ordered ordinances to\nthat effect drawn and has ordered\nthe work to proceed at once.\n\n\nThe improvement will run from\nMonroe street west to Hangman\ncreek, from the Spokane river\nsouth to Fifth avenue, and will cost\naround $500, 900."
